node.title: Holt
node.plot: On the 17th of December 1967, Australia's Prime Minister, Harold Holt, disappeared without a trace - but not originally. Someone wants the Prime Minister dead and only time travel will allow it.

node.title: How the Grinch Stole Christmas!
node.plot: Bitter and hateful, the Grinch is irritated at the thought of the nearby village having a happy time celebrating Christmas. So disguised as Santa Claus, with his dog made to look like a reindeer, he raids the village to steal all the Christmas things. The village is sure to have a sad Christmas this year.
